text: Pogonocherus arizonicus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gottlieb August Wilhelm Herrich-Schäffer in 1908. It is known from Mexico and the United States.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus arizonicus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1908
